      "projectDescription": "DSSO as linker, study of protein-protein interaction by LC-MSMS",
      "sampleProcessingProtocol": "DSSO was added to protein complex, linked for 1h, qunched by tris. Cysteine residues were reduced with 10 mM DTT at 56\u2103 for 30 min and alkylated with 50 mM iodoacetamide for 30 min at room temperature, dark. Sample were digested by Chymotrypsin at 37 \u2103, pH 8, overnight, peptides desalting with C18 column, LC-MSMS analysis.",
